As if things weren't amazing enough already, you can even see a counter. The counter is vast. On the counter you make out a fried red potato, a red apple, a raw purple potato, a cookbook and a knife. You bend down to tie your shoe. When you stand up, you notice a stove. The stove is conventional. Looks like someone's already been here and taken everything off it, though. Oh! Why couldn't there just be stuff on it?

You bend down to tie your shoe. When you stand up, you notice a stove. The stove is conventional. Looks like someone's already been here and taken everything off it, though. Oh! Why couldn't there just be stuff on it?
